  "title": "Electrical Engineer",
  "description": "<ul><li>6Days - 8.30 - 6.30 & 24Hours Standy <br /></li><li>Excellent in reading and understanding electrical schematic diagram</li><li>Analyse and interpret the technical specifications and blueprints</li><li>Ensure that the project is within the stipulated timeline, budget, quality standard, and high safety</li><li>Knowledgeable of local codes and regulations for electrical building services</li><li>Facilitate the construction and installation of the electrical equipment and its components in accordance with the specifications and standards</li><li>Checks and reviews detailed electrical construction drawings to meet design standards and minimize errors</li><li>Responsible for the analysis, definition, design, construction, testing, installation, modification, and maintenance of automated machines, containing software as the major component</li><li>Perform electrical and electronic conceptual details design work.</li><li>Liaise with clients, consultants, and relevant authorities on their engineering request</li><li>Design, Engineer, and provide optimized solutions to meet project & client requirements</li><li>Support the site team in resolving issues during installation, testing & commissioning</li><li>Any ad-hoc duties assigned by management</li></ul>",
